            {"q_en": "What weapons did his army mostly have?", "q_hi": "उनकी सेना के मुख्य हथियार?", "options_en": ["Rifles","Bows & arrows","Tanks","Cannons"], "options_hi": ["राइफ़लें","धनुष-बाण","टैंक","तोपें"], "answer": 1},
