            {"q_en": "Which forest law angered him?", "q_hi": "कौन सा वन क़ानून उन्हें भड़काया?", "options_en": ["Madras Forest Act 1882","Salt Act","Vernacular Press Act","Rowlatt Act"], "options_hi": ["मद्रास वन क़ानून 1882","नमक क़ानून","वर्नाक्युलर प्रेस","रौलट"], "answer": 0},
