            {"q_en": "She rejected what offer?", "q_hi": "किस प्रस्ताव को ठुकराया?", "options_en": ["British pension","Crown of India","Indian flag","Tea trade"], "options_hi": ["अंग्रेज़ी पेंशन","भारत का ताज","भारतीय झंडा","चाय व्यापार"], "answer": 0},
