            {"q_en": "She is the first Karnataka woman fighter honoured in?", "q_hi": "कर्नाटक की पहली महिला सेनानी जिनकी प्रतिमा कहाँ?", "options_en": ["Indian Parliament","UK","UN","Vatican"], "options_hi": ["भारतीय संसद","ब्रिटेन","UN","वेटिकन"], "answer": 0},
